public class AeCorrelatedReceive
extends AeAbstractQueuedObject

Base class for correlated queue objects. No behavior here, just providing the common fields and getters and setters.

isCorrelated

public boolean isCorrelated()
A queue object that is correlated has its correlation data participate in the evaluation of equality. Queue objects that are not correlated will only perform the comparison against the plink, port type, and operation.
